      "totalCount": 6624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8548&rangeEnd=8611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=8548&rangeEnd=8611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_22_9099-9180",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "9099-9180",
      "markText": "我们越是忙碌，越会高看自己，认为自己对他人来说不可或缺。我们无法陪伴亲人朋友，不知疲倦，没日没夜，只管四处救火，不给自己留下喘息的时间。这就是现代社会的成功典型。",
      "totalCount": 5376,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=9099&rangeEnd=9180",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=9099&rangeEnd=9180"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_10956-11011",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "10956-11011",
      "markText": "多数人花费太多时间处理眼下的危机，应付他人的期望，而不是思维清醒地思考什么最重要，并以此为指导做出谨慎的选择。",
      "totalCount": 4800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10956&rangeEnd=11011",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10956&rangeEnd=11011"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_22_1814-1863",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "1814-1863",
      "markText": "持续健身能带来身心改善，但若停止一周，曾经的改善就会大幅退步，只要停止4周，这种改善就会完全消失。",
      "totalCount": 4302,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1814&rangeEnd=1863",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=1814&rangeEnd=1863"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_935-967",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "935-967",
      "markText": "我们对广度的热爱超过了对深度的关注，注重反应速度却不愿深入思考。",
      "totalCount": 4270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=935&rangeEnd=967",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=935&rangeEnd=967"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_1912-1984",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1912-1984",
      "markText": "精力，而非时间， 是高效表现的基础",
      "totalCount": 4173,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1912&rangeEnd=1984",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1912&rangeEnd=1984"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_10223-10274",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "10223-10274",
      "markText": "仪式习惯的优势在于，确保我们在非必要情况下尽量减少意识精力的消耗，让它可以节省下来用在其他需要的方面。",
      "totalCount": 4140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10223&rangeEnd=10274",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10223&rangeEnd=10274"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_446-475",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "446-475",
      "markText": "精力就是做事情的能力。包括体能、情感、思维、意志四个方面。",
      "totalCount": 3808,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=475"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_29_8733-8750",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "8733-8750",
      "markText": "你希望你的墓志铭如何总结你的人生？",
      "totalCount": 3504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8733&rangeEnd=8750",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8733&rangeEnd=8750"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_29_8623-8651",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "8623-8651",
      "markText": "想想你最敬重的一个人，描述他/她身上你最钦佩的3种品质。",
      "totalCount": 3472,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8623&rangeEnd=8651",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8623&rangeEnd=8651"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_2551-2643",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "2551-2643",
      "markText": "一天只有固定的24小时，但精力的储备与质量却没有定数。精力是我们最宝贵的资源。我们越是本着负责的态度对待它，越能变得多产而高效。反之，越是怨天尤人，我们的精力会变得越是消极、质量低下。",
      "totalCount": 2839,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2551&rangeEnd=2643",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=2551&rangeEnd=2643"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_24_6057-6121",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "6057-6121",
      "markText": "我们都赞同“80/20”的原则：如果你摄入的80%的食物都是健康而高效的，剩下的20%可以是你喜欢的任何食物，只要份量控制得当。",
      "totalCount": 2464,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6057&rangeEnd=6121",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6057&rangeEnd=6121"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_9403-9457",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "9403-9457",
      "markText": "任何会导致不适的压力都可能帮助我们提升能力——在体能、思维、情感和意志上都是如此——只要事后得到有效的恢复。",
      "totalCount": 2448,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9403&rangeEnd=9457",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=9403&rangeEnd=9457"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_22_558-622",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "558-622",
      "markText": "事实上，人需要顺应消耗与恢复的节奏，运动与休息的交替进行可以最大限度提高表现。“张弛有度”是全情投入、维持机能和保持健康的关键。",
      "totalCount": 2353,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=558&rangeEnd=622",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=558&rangeEnd=622"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_22_14338-14376",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "14338-14376",
      "markText": "能力拓展的关键在于，既要超出日常的极限，又要定期休整恢复，二者兼备才能成长。",
      "totalCount": 2301,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=14338&rangeEnd=14376",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=14338&rangeEnd=14376"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_29_8553-8590",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "8553-8590",
      "markText": "如果现在就是人生的尽头，你学到的最重要的3件事是什么？为什么它们如此重要？",
      "totalCount": 2288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8553&rangeEnd=8590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=8553&rangeEnd=8590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_20_10563-10598",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "10563-10598",
      "markText": "我们发现，为了确保全情投入，建立良好的仪式习惯是精力管理的最有效方式。",
      "totalCount": 2240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33091654&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10563&rangeEnd=10598",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4263296071f8f0464264d41?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=10563&rangeEnd=10598"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33091654_22_9800-9885",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "9800-9885",
